s=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> bashr : \u000A  <span><span class=\"label\">size</span>:<a href=\"../../../../../../codex/Units/In_bits/index.html#type-t\">Units.In_bits.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span>(<a href=\"../index.html#type-binary\">binary</a>, <a href=\"../index.html#type-binary\">binary</a>, <a href=\"../index.html#type-binary\">binary</a>)</span> <a href=\"../../../../../../codex/Domains/Sig/Context_Arity_Forward/index.html#type-ar2\">Domains.Sig.Context_Arity_Forward(Context).ar2</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Arithmetic shift right: fill with the most significant bit.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-blshr\"><a href=\"#val-blshr\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> blshr : \u000A  <span><span class=\"label\">size</span>:<a href=\"../../../../../../codex/Units/In_bits/index.html#type-t\">Units.In_bits.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span>(<a href=\"../index.html#type-binary\">binary</a>, <a href=\"../index.html#type-binary\">binary</a>, <a href=\"../index.html#type-binary\">binary</a>)</span> <a href=\"../../../../../../codex/Domains/Sig/Context_Arity_Forward/index.html#type-ar2\">Domains.Sig.Context_Arity_Forward(Context).ar2</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Logical shift right: fill with 0.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-beq\"><a href=\"#val-beq\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> beq : \u000A  <span><span class=\"label\">size</span>:<a href=\"../../../../../../codex/Units/In_bits/index.html#type-t\">Units.In_bits.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span>(<a href=\"../index.html#type-binary\">binary</a>, <a href=\"../index.html#type-binary\">binary</a>, <a href=\"../index.html#type-boolean\">boolean</a>)</span> <a href=\"../../../../../../codex/Domains/Sig/Context_Arity_Forward/index.html#type-ar2\">Domains.Sig.Context_Arity_Forward(Context).ar2</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Bitvector equality</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-bisle\"><a href=\"#val-bisle\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> bisle : \u000A  <span><span class=\"label\">size</span>:<a href=\"../../../../../../codex/Units/In_bits/index.html#type-t\">Units.In_bits.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span>(<a href=\"../index.html#type-binary\">binary</a>, <a href=\"../index.html#type-binary\">binary</a>, <a href=\"../index.html#type-boolean\">boolean</a>)</span> <a href=\"../../../../../../codex/Domains/Sig/Context_Arity_Forward/index.html#type-ar2\">Domains.Sig.Context_Arity_Forward(Context).ar2</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Signed comparison between two bitvectors (using less-or-equal <code>&lt;=</code>). Bitvectors are interpreted as integers in <code class=\"odoc-katex-math\">[-2^{size-1}..-2^{size-1}-1]</code> using two's complement.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-biule\"><a href=\"#val-biule\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> biule : \u000A  <span><span class=\"label\">size</span>:<a href=\"../../../../../../codex/Units/In_bits/index.html#type-t\">Units.In_bits.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span>(<a href=\"../index.html#type-binary\">binary</a>, <a href=\"../index.html#type-binary\">binary</a>, <a href=\"../index.html#type-boolean\">boolean</a>)</span> <a href=\"../../../../../../codex/Domains/Sig/Context_Arity_Forward/index.html#type-ar2\">Domains.Sig.Context_Arity_Forward(Context).ar2</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Unsigned comparison between two bitvectors (using less-or-equal <code